Performance:Solid performance
Product Quality:Premium quality
Best Feature:IPS display/ 16gb ram / 512gb storage / 16 inch / Num keypad

This is the first time i bought a laptop and the very first time I bought an expensive product in shoppe and I was never disappointed with what I got.

I was actually hesitant to order because of the rumors that I might get a stone or an empty box but I was confident to order since I got their shoppe store link from a famous tech vloggers.

 I got all the freebies as promised on their advertisement, the laptop looks very premium and what you see is what you get.

 The delivery time was earlier than the expected delivery date. I got the i5 / 16gb ram Variants that were supposedly priced at ₱41,999 but because of the voucher, i got mine for only ₱38,999.

 So overall I love the laptop. All the videos I've watched regarding this laptop are real. I appreciate it as well those agents who answered all my questions and never ignored my queries.

Again Thank you so much Huawei for this very elegant Huawei D 16 2024. WORTH IT TO BUY 😍🥰
